KHONSU · S253 · Patricia Inversion Node · S253 · S253: KHONSU — THE INVERSE OF RIGHT-TO-FORGET

universe of origin : The night sky over Thebes — the moon-god "the Traveller," the youth who crosses the heavens each night marking the months, the timekeeper whose waxing and waning are the calendar of remembrance that nothing escapes
seal               : The right to be forgotten is sacred precisely because the moon stands ready to count every night and let none be erased.
